'''班·史奈澤'''（{{lang-en|'''Ben Schnetzer'''}}，{{bd|1990年|2月8日}}）美國新生代演員。<br />

班·史奈澤生於紐約並於當地長大。他是演員 [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Schnetzer Stephen Schnetzer] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Schnetzer |date=20160921080126 }} 及 [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nancy_Snyder Nancy Snyder] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nancy_Snyder |date=20160920192139 }} 的兒子。畢業於英國倫敦 Guildhall音樂戲劇學院（[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guildhall_School_of_Music_and_Drama Guildhall School of Music and Drama] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guildhall_School_of_Music_and_Drama |date=20160702041011 }}）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/03/movies/ben-schnetzer-on-the-book-thief.html|title=First Big Role, Right Out of School|date=2013-11-03|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2015-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150422104301/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/03/movies/ben-schnetzer-on-the-book-thief.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <br />
班·史奈澤1990年出生於美國紐約的演員家庭中，耳濡目染之下便在11歲時踏上表演之路，2007年演出他的第一部電影《Ben’s Plan》於2010年在美劇「法律與秩序(台譯：法網遊龍)」(''[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Law_%26_Order Law & Order] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Law_%26_Order |date=20160719160603 }}'')單集演出，扮演Dustin Henry一角，同年亦於美劇「快樂鎮(台譯：快樂鎮疑案)」(''[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Happy_Town_(TV_series) Happy Town] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Happy_Town_(TV_series) |date=20160806181744 }}'')擔任聯合主演，扮演Andrew Haplin一角(演出共8集)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/tv-radio/happy-town-not-so-much-243981/|title='Happy Town' ... not so much|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2012-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028051026/http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/tv-radio/happy-town-not-so-much-243981/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。<br />
班·史奈澤於2013年電影「偷書賊」(''[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Book_Thief_(film) The Book Thief] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Book_Thief_(film) |date=20160704172222 }}'')扮演Max Vandenburg開啟他的電影事業。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/the-book-thief-review-1200694271/|title=Film Review: ‘The Book Thief’|first=Dennis|last=Harvey|date=2013-10-04|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806103918/http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/the-book-thief-review-1200694271/|dead-url=no}}</ref><br />
班·史奈澤於2014年出演真實事件改編LGSM(Lesbians and Gays Support the Miners)題材的電影[[:骄傲_(电影)|驕傲(台譯驕傲大聯盟)]]([[pride|pride]])扮演同性戀者馬克·阿什頓([https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark_Ashton Mark Ashton] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark_Ashton |date=20160702021956 }})一角及[[:高富帥俱樂部|:高富帥俱樂部]]([[The_Riot_Club|The Riot Club]])Dimitri Mitropoulos一角。他在驕傲該片演出表現亮眼，入圍2014年英國獨立製片獎「最佳男配角獎」及「新人獎」獎項<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bifa.film/awards/winners/2014|title=Winners - Awards 2014 - BIFA - The British Independent Film Awards|first=|last=BIFA|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119163839/https://www.bifa.film/awards/winners/2014|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。<br />於2016年6月上映電影[[魔獸：崛起|魔獸：崛起]](WARCRAFT: The Beginning)出演被肯德托(The  Kirin Tor)訓練要接替麥迪文成為艾澤拉斯守護者(Guardian of Tirisfal )的見習守護者，卻因理念而背棄誓言離開肯德托前往風暴國的年輕法師[[:魔兽系列角色列表#.E5.8D.A1.E5.BE.B7.E5.8A.A0|卡德加(Khadgar)]]一角。<br />
2015年2月有消息釋出，班·史奈澤將參與預訂於2016年9月上映電影「[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Snowden_(film) Snowden] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Snowden_(film) |date=20160818160927 }}」(暫譯史諾登)演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/pride-actor-joins-oliver-stones-edward-snowden-film-1201433828/|title=‘Pride’ Actor Joins Oliver Stone’s Edward Snowden Film|first=Justin|last=Kroll|date=2015-02-13|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423134310/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/pride-actor-joins-oliver-stones-edward-snowden-film-1201433828/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
